 13/8 /18 Framervill Found Braithwait and visit his post which were connect by a wire . The post were small one at the rear of some were dead Australian . Found all the chap in good heart until I reach A Co. where the loss of a tin of stew had upset their moral altogeth . I rous certain peopl up over this occur and the men receiv an extra issu of porridg to make up for it . Short after the right post of C Co. was struck by a whizzbang and 1 kill 6 wound was the result . Call and saw Davi befor return to H.Q . and to sleep. Got up at noon a fine warm and peac day . Expect to advanc my line tonight and also the have to do a sidestep. Took Sutherland with me and made a reconnaiss of the
